channelEmbed.description:
I'm **Trivia Bot**. I was made with BCFD and JavaScript. I'm open-sourced, so if you want to copy my commands, feel free to do so by visiting [GitHub](https://github.com/Gl1tch3dL1m3/trivia-bcfd/tree/main).

My commands:
`q?gen` - Generate a question.
`q?ans <answer's letter>` - Answer a question.

*Don't include <>.*
